---
import Base from "~/layouts/Base.astro";
import { SITE } from "~/lib/seo";

const structuredData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  name: "Project Estimation Form",
  description: "Dapatkan estimasi proyek dengan mengisi form brief singkat.",
  url: `${SITE.url}/brief`,
};
---

<Base
  title="Project Estimation Form"
  description="Dapatkan estimasi proyek dengan mengisi form brief singkat."
  structuredData={structuredData}
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: "Project Brief", url: "/brief" }]}
>
  <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-4xl gap-10 px-6 pb-24 pt-28">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent">Project Brief</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl text-text">Request Project Estimation</h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-base text-text2">
        Isi form singkat di bawah untuk mendapatkan estimasi proyek. Saya akan merespons dalam 1â€“2
        hari kerja dengan estimasi timeline, budget range, dan rekomendasi pendekatan terbaik.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid gap-8 rounded-3xl border border-divider/40 bg-surface/80 p-8 shadow-soft">
      <div class="space-y-3 rounded-xl border border-accent/20 bg-accent/5 p-4">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text">ðŸ’¡ Tips untuk mendapat estimasi akurat:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 text-sm text-text2">
          <li>â€¢ Jelaskan tujuan utama produk/project</li>
          <li>â€¢ List fitur-fitur yang dibutuhkan</li>
          <li>â€¢ Sebutkan referensi produk serupa (jika ada)</li>
          <li>â€¢ Budget range dan timeline ideal kamu</li>
          <li>â€¢ Tech stack preferensi (opsional)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <form class="grid gap-6" method="post" action="https://formsubmit.co/noorwahid717@gmail.com">
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Project Estimation Request" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://noahisme.vercel.app/brief?success=true" />
        <input type="text" name="_honey" class="hidden" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" />

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="name">Nama / Perusahaan*</label>
          <input
            class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            type="text"
            id="name"
            name="name"
            required
            autocomplete="name"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="email">Email*</label>
          <input
            class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="phone">Nomor WhatsApp (opsional)</label>
          <input
            class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            type="tel"
            id="phone"
            name="phone"
            autocomplete="tel"
            placeholder="+62..."
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="project_type">Tipe Project*</label>
          <select
            class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            id="project_type"
            name="project_type"
            required
          >
            <option value="">Pilih tipe project</option>
            <option value="web_app">Web Application</option>
            <option value="mobile_app">Mobile App</option>
            <option value="landing_page">Landing Page / Marketing Site</option>
            <option value="ecommerce">E-commerce</option>
            <option value="saas">SaaS Product</option>
            <option value="dashboard">Dashboard / Admin Panel</option>
            <option value="api">API / Backend</option>
            <option value="other">Lainnya</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="description">Deskripsi Project*</label>
          <textarea
            class="focus-outline min-h-[160px] rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            id="description"
            name="description"
            required
            placeholder="Jelaskan tujuan utama, target user, dan apa yang ingin dicapai..."
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="features">Fitur Utama*</label>
          <textarea
            class="focus-outline min-h-[120px] rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            id="features"
            name="features"
            required
            placeholder="Contoh:
- User authentication (email & social login)
- Dashboard analytics
- Payment integration
- Admin panel"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="reference"
            >Referensi Produk (opsional)</label
          >
          <input
            class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            type="text"
            id="reference"
            name="reference"
            placeholder="URL atau nama produk serupa"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="grid gap-2">
            <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="budget">Budget Range*</label>
            <select
              class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
              id="budget"
              name="budget"
              required
            >
              <option value="">Pilih range</option>
              <option value="< 10jt">&lt; Rp 10 juta</option>
              <option value="10-25jt">Rp 10â€“25 juta</option>
              <option value="25-50jt">Rp 25â€“50 juta</option>
              <option value="50-100jt">Rp 50â€“100 juta</option>
              <option value="> 100jt">&gt; Rp 100 juta</option>
              <option value="flexible">Fleksibel</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-2">
            <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="timeline">Timeline Target*</label>
            <select
              class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
              id="timeline"
              name="timeline"
              required
            >
              <option value="">Pilih timeline</option>
              <option value="urgent">Urgent (&lt; 2 minggu)</option>
              <option value="1-month">1 bulan</option>
              <option value="2-3-months">2â€“3 bulan</option>
              <option value="3-6-months">3â€“6 bulan</option>
              <option value="> 6-months">&gt; 6 bulan</option>
              <option value="flexible">Fleksibel</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="tech_stack"
            >Tech Stack Preferensi (opsional)</label
          >
          <input
            class="focus-outline rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            type="text"
            id="tech_stack"
            name="tech_stack"
            placeholder="Contoh: Next.js, Node.js, PostgreSQL, AWS"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-text" for="additional"
            >Info Tambahan (opsional)</label
          >
          <textarea
            class="focus-outline min-h-[100px] rounded-md border border-divider/60 bg-bg/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text"
            id="additional"
            name="additional"
            placeholder="Design sudah ada? Ada tim internal? Target market? dll."></textarea>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="group inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-accent/90 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/25 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          <span>Kirim Brief & Dapatkan Estimasi</span>
          <svg
            class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>

        <p class="text-center text-sm text-text2">
          Atau jadwalkan <a href="/book/intro" class="text-accent hover:underline"
            >Intro Call (20m)</a
          > untuk diskusi langsung
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-divider/40 bg-bg/40 p-6">
      <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Apa yang terjadi selanjutnya?</h3>
      <ol class="grid gap-3 text-sm text-text2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-xs font-medium text-accent"
            >1</span
          >
          <span>Saya review brief kamu dan estimasi scope pekerjaan</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-xs font-medium text-accent"
            >2</span
          >
          <span
            >Kirim estimasi timeline, budget, dan pendekatan yang direkomendasikan (1â€“2 hari kerja)</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-xs font-medium text-accent"
            >3</span
          >
          <span>Jika cocok, kita jadwalkan Discovery Workshop untuk detail scope</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-xs font-medium text-accent"
            >4</span
          >
          <span>Mulai development! ðŸš€</span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
